definitions.definition: A term for a marijuana cigarette ('joint').
examples: "I went outside to smoke myself a J " — Paul Simon , from the song "Late in the Evening" from the album, "One Trick Pony."

definitions.definition: An alternative version of i , the positive square root of -1; used in the context of electronics.
The second unit vector , after i
